data.name: label3.ToolTip
data.value: To add a community-provided language, click on "Add" and select the language's .ini file. To make your own translation, click on 'Modify' and then save as your-language-name. Refer to the documentation, Part V Section [10.2] for more help.

data.name: label4.ToolTip
data.value: Click on 'Modify' to edit the selected theme's settings. To add a community-provided theme, click on 'Add' and select the theme's zip file. To make your own, refer to the documentation, Part V Section [10.3].
